label: "Fiftieth Anniversary. South Carolina Federation of Colored Women's Club. 1909-1959"
description: South Carolina Federation of Colored Women's Clubs' Fiftieth Anniversary publication. Affiliated with National Association of Colored Women's Clubs. Publication contains photographs of club members in various locations around South Carolina, information on members and subgroups, and advertisements.
